Package
Description
technology.sola.json
This package provides the core classes for sola-json.
technology.sola.json.builder
This package provides builders for JsonArray and JsonObject.
technology.sola.json.exception
This package provides various exceptions for errors that may happen during various sola-json operations.
technology.sola.json.mapper
This package provides classes for mapping between Java objects and JSON.
technology.sola.json.parser
This package provides functionality for parsing JSON utilizing a SolaJsonTokenizer.
technology.sola.json.serializer
This package provides functionality for serializing JsonElement, JsonObject and JsonArray.
technology.sola.json.tokenizer
This package provides functionality for tokenizing a JSON string.
